              "chord": "",
              "text": "In her are both Your dear self and Your fullness;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That is what makes her my aspiration, Lord!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All will be new, Lord, because You are present;"
